        <cell>
          <image source="chapter-6/horizontal_asymptote_right_below.png">
            <shortdescription>Approach b from below as x approaches infinity.</shortdescription>
          </image>
        </cell>
      </row>
      <row>
        <cell><m>y \to b</m> as <m>x \to -\infty</m></cell>\
        <cell>
          <image source="chapter-6/horizontal_asymptote_left_above.png">
            <shortdescription>Approach b from above as x as approaches negative infinity.</shortdescription>
          </image>
        </cell>
      </row>
      <row>
        <cell><m>y \to b</m> as <m>x \to \pm\infty</m></cell>
        <cell>
          <image source="chapter-6/arrow_y_b.png">
            <shortdescription>Approach the same horizontal line in both directions.</shortdescription>
          </image>
